{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a682dd2351","title":"在陈正人对《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》第三稿的意见信上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"635db6dab7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"a682dd2351"}],"tags":[{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"f508083de6","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈正人，当时任中共中央农村工作部副部长。"},{"id":"d8c5045c24","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈佰达，当时任中共中央政治研究室主任、毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"a1594dfd8e","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈正人1957年6月7日写给毛泽东的对《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》第三稿的意见信。信中建议在稿中“大规模的群众性的阶级斗争已经结束”这一句前面加上“革命时期”4个字。并说，“我理解这句话的意思，是指两个革命——人民民主革命、社会主义革命——已经基本胜利，革命（社会改革）已基本结束，我们已进入社会主义建设时期，但阶级斗争仍然存在。这种斗争，不但表现为长期的思想上的斗争，也表现为政治的及其他形式的斗争（如经济的）”。后来公开发表的《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》一文采纳了这一建议。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0cb79434f6","type":"title","text":"在陈正人”对《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》第三稳的意见信上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"},{"id":"f508083de6","type":"paragraph","text":"陈伯达同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"},{"id":"d8c5045c24","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请参药。如果文件今晚搞不完，明日下午二时交我也","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"},{"id":"a1594dfd8e","type":"subtitle","text":"可以。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"},{"id":"8347ce52f0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"},{"id":"482b278634","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351"}],"page":{"id":"c36be2b9cb","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"a682dd2351","start":116,"end":116}}}},"__N_SSG":true}